@inveda.in - Ask them your query

www.inveda.in

👉🏻Give your chemical products a break and incorporate Inveda’s Pigmentation Free Skin Care Kit to improve your skin.

Step 1- Cleanse your face & neck with Inveda’s Neem and Gotukula Cleanser, Gotukula face wash removes all deep seated impurities from the skin, stops acne from growing up & leaves skin fresh and rejuvenated. For all skin types. Use it in the morning and evening

Step 2- Apply Whitening and Depigmentation Cream which lightens the pigments by absorbing into your skin and removing signs of pigmentation like discoloured skin patches.

Step 3- Application of Anti-Pigmentation blend will result in cure of the discoloured patches as it evenly balances the presence of melanin pigment in your skin. Mix it with whitening & de pigmentation cream & apply. Use it at night

Step 4- Finish this easy process with Inveda’s Sunscreen Cream Gel SPF 30 in the morning which effectively protects your skin for harmful UVA/UVB rays of the sun.

I hope wherever you are, you’re alright, whatever problems you’re facing, goes away and whatever you wanna achieve, you thrive for it!✨
Sending love and happiness for all of you!🤍🦋
Can’t wait to see what 2021 holds for us...🥳
